PHASE 13 OBJECTIVE
============================================================

Build the mobile and public developer platform layer for zDash.

Main goals:

1. Add Expo React Native mobile app
2. Add mobile authentication flow
3. Add mobile secure token storage
4. Add mobile dashboard overview
5. Add mobile risk/halt controls
