20. Add partner API rate limits and usage metering
21. Add partner audit logs
22. Add tests for mobile API support, partner API security, SDKs, sandbox, rate limits, and tenant isolation

IMPORTANT SAFETY RULES:
- Do not enable live trading by default.
- Do not enable real IoT actions by default.
- Do not enable real social posting by default.
- Do not bypass Guardian risk checks.
- Do not bypass content approval checks.
- Do not bypass tenant isolation.
- Do not bypass billing entitlements.
- Do not bypass governance policies.
- Mobile app must not expose secrets.
- Partner API must never expose internal secrets.
- Partner API must not allow live trading, real IoT, or real social posting unless explicitly allowed by strict entitlement, approval, and production safety checks.
- Sandbox mode must be default for public developer examples.
- SDK examples must use sandbox and dry-run calls only.
- API keys must be hashed at rest.
- Raw API keys must only be shown once at creation.
- Partner webhooks must DLP-scan outbound payloads.
- Rate limits must fail safely.

