CONFIG REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Update root `.env.example`:

MOBILE_API_ENABLED=true
MOBILE_PUSH_ENABLED=false
MOBILE_PUSH_PROVIDER=mock
MOBILE_PUSH_DRY_RUN=true
MOBILE_SESSION_REFRESH_ENABLED=true

DEVELOPER_PLATFORM_ENABLED=true
PUBLIC_DEVELOPER_PORTAL_ENABLED=true
PARTNER_API_ENABLED=true
PARTNER_API_SANDBOX_DEFAULT=true
PARTNER_API_FAIL_CLOSED=true

API_KEYS_ENABLED=true
API_KEY_HASH_PEPPER=change-me-api-key-pepper
API_KEY_PREFIX=zdash
API_KEY_DEFAULT_EXPIRES_DAYS=365
API_KEY_MAX_ACTIVE_PER_ORG=10

APP_CREDENTIALS_ENABLED=true
OAUTH_CLIENT_CREDENTIALS_SHELL_ENABLED=true

PARTNER_RATE_LIMIT_ENABLED=true
PARTNER_RATE_LIMIT_PER_MINUTE=60
PARTNER_RATE_LIMIT_PER_DAY=5000
PARTNER_RATE_LIMIT_FAIL_CLOSED=true

SANDBOX_ENABLED=true
SANDBOX_AUTO_PROVISION=true
SANDBOX_DATA_RESET_ENABLED=true
SANDBOX_DEFAULT_PLAN=starter
SANDBOX_FORCE_DRY_RUN=true

SDK_GENERATION_ENABLED=true
OPENAPI_EXPORT_ENABLED=true
OPENAPI_PUBLIC_SPEC_PATH=docs/developer/openapi-public.json

PARTNER_WEBHOOKS_ENABLED=true
PARTNER_WEBHOOKS_DRY_RUN=true
PARTNER_WEBHOOK_SIGNING_ENABLED=true
PARTNER_WEBHOOK_DELIVERY_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=10
PARTNER_WEBHOOK_MAX_RETRIES=3

Rules:
- Mobile push must be disabled/mock by default.
- Developer platform must default to sandbox and dry-run.
- API keys must be hashed with strong one-way hashing.
- API key pepper must not be logged.
- Default API key pepper must be rejected in production.
- Partner API rate limits must be enabled by default.
- Sandbox must force DRY_RUN=true.
- Public OpenAPI spec must exclude internal/admin-only routes.
- Partner webhooks must be dry-run by default.
- Raw webhook signing secrets must not be returned after creation.

Update mobile `.env.example`:

EXPO_PUBLIC_APP_NAME=zDash Mobile
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000
EXPO_PUBLIC_ENABLE_MOCK_FALLBACK=true
EXPO_PUBLIC_POLL_INTERVAL_MS=5000
EXPO_PUBLIC_SHOW_SAFETY_BANNERS=true
EXPO_PUBLIC_ENABLE_PUSH=false

