============================================================
PARTNER WEBHOOK REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Create:

backend/app/developer/webhook_subscriptions.py

Methods:
- create_subscription(request)
- list_subscriptions()
- update_subscription(subscription_id, patch)
- delete_subscription(subscription_id)
- deliver_event(event_type, payload, tenant_context)
- list_deliveries(subscription_id=None)
- retry_delivery(delivery_id)

Rules:
- Dry-run by default.
- DLP-scan payload before delivery.
- Sign payload if signing enabled.
- Never include secrets in payload.
- Delivery failure must not crash app.
- Delivery attempts capped.
- Delivery logs tenant-scoped.

